          <description><![CDATA[
            <ul>
<li>There apparently are wall posts. How do these federate?</li>
<li>There’s <code>zot:commentPolicy</code> to limit who can comment on a post. What are the possible values of this field? Is it only set per post, or it can have a default value per actor?</li>
